## Command Reference

`python -m cli [--db <path>] <command> <subcommand> [options]`

### workflow
```
create --title "..." [--source-file <path>]
list | show | delete <W-ID>
import <W-ID> --structure '<json>' | --structure-file <path>
restart <W-ID> [--clear-ops]
set-order <T-ID> ... | set-parallel --group <name> <T-ID> ... | add-dep <T-ID> --depends-on <T-ID>
next | current
```

### epic / task
```
epic create --title "..." | list | show <E-ID> | update <E-ID> --status <status> | delete <E-ID>
task create --parent <E-ID|T-ID> --title "..."
task list [--epic <E-ID>] [--status <status>] | show <T-ID>
task update <T-ID> --status <todo|in_progress|interrupted|done|cancelled> [--interrupt "reason"]
task delete <T-ID>
```

### plan
```
plan update --changes '{"create":[...],"update":[...],"delete":[...]}' [--workflow <W-ID>]
```

### op / resource / query
```
op start|progress|complete|error|interrupt <T-ID> --summary "..." [--platform ...]
op log [--task <T-ID>]
resource add <T-ID> --path <path> --type <type> --desc "..."
resource list --task <T-ID> | --workflow <W-ID> [--type <type>]
query show [--workflow <W-ID>] | status | tasks [--status <status>]
```

### objective / setting / project
```
objective create --title "..." --milestone "..." | --due-date YYYY-MM-DD
objective list | update <O-ID> --status done
setting set <key> <value> | get <key> | list | delete <key>
project checkpoint [--note "..."] | checkpoint list | rollback --checkpoint <id> | restart [--clear-ops]
```

